When her four year old daughter informs her a sick man is in their yard, Honor Gillette rushes out to help him. Dangerous, desperate, and armed, he promises Honor that she and her daughter won't be hurt as long as she does everything he asks. She has no choice but to accept him at his word.

title: Cinta
description:
cinta? 
Apa itu cinta?
Yang aku tau, cinta adalah sebuah penyakit di bagian terdalam organ tubuh kita yang terletak di sebelah jantung.
Sakit, satu kata yang sangat tepat untuk menggambarkan definisi apa itu cinta. Bagi sebagian orang, Cinta itu indah, cinta itu bisa membuat mereka bahagia. Iya itu bagi mereka yang beruntung, bagi mereka yang cintanya terbalas. Jangan kalian fikir cinta itu seperti gulali. Manis di awal sampai akhir. Blur banget kalo Cinta itu seperti itu.
Namaku Aggie, tepatnya Aggie Amanda yang berarti pantas di cintai dan di inginkan, seorang gadis biasa dari kalangan menangah kebawah, salah satu keryawan di perusahaan yang lumayan terkemuka, dan selalu gagal dalam ber Cinta.
Blushit banget kalo Cinta itu indah, iya indah di awal dan di akhir? Jangan Tanya lagi. Lihat saja mereka yang selalu mengumbar kemesraan di sosial media, kita lihat tak lama dari itu mungkin kabar duka ankan terpampang jelas di kolom status sosial media masing masing memenuhi semua bernda sosial media dengan ocehan ocehan galau tak berkelas ala jomblo jaman now.
Dulu aku begitu sangat memuja Cinta, karena Cinta aku bisa bertemu denganya, dia yang sekarang ini ingin sekali aku enyahkan dari fikiranku.
Karena cinta aku bisa mengenalnya, mengenal kepribadianya, mengenal sifatnya dan sangat mengenal bagaimana cara dia begitu lembut mematahkan Cintaku.
Dulu aku selalu memanggilnya, Jodohku. Ya itu dulu beberapa tahun yang lalu, disaat aku masih menduduki bangku kuliah di Universitas yang sama denganya. Di saat Cinta masih begitu Indah untukku hingga tanpa sadar aku sudah terlalu dalam tenggalam di lautan penuh kesakitan, Pesanku untuk Cinta. LUPAKAN atau PERGI

title: Nicole in the Middle
description:
September Gray, editor of both her school's newspaper and literary magazine, just wants to make it through her sophomore year and get out into the real world. Captivated in a penitentiary known as high school she finds it easier to be an introvert and hide behind music and words. 

On her 16th birthday, she goes from being behind the scenes to the subject of the front page story. Not sure how to deal with everything she starts a blog with a pseudonym called "Nicole in the Middle".  Her alter ego is her only sense of control now, and that is threatened when September's blog raises in popularity. Everyone wants to know who Nicole is. And according to doctors, her time is running out. 

Reader beware, for the plot twists will make you pull out your hair. A contemporary suspense story with a dash of fan fiction and a twist of lime.

When I was young, I used to read to my younger siblings. They liked superhero stories the best. They like hearing about batman and robin, the avengers, the teen titans, anything they could get their hands on.

  That changed when I was dragged away from my home in Sweeny , Texas.

title: My Bossy Boyfriend (MBB)
description:
Aries Motenire,a 23 years old lady.Maganda at  mayaman.Panganay sa apat na magkakapatid.Pareho silang mga dependent ng mga kapatid niya.They chose to live dependently than to live like a princess.Ayaw nilang umasa sa mga magulang nila.
"Dapat matuto tayong buhayin ang sarili natin.H'wag yung iaasa natin lahat kay Mom at Dad lahat ng needs natin"
Iyan ang mga katagang palaging sinasabi ni Aries sa mga nakababatang kapatid niya.Bagama't pasaway ang bunso nilang si Izra,pilit pa rin nila itong iniintindi sa kadahilanang college student lamang ito.
Nagtatrabaho si Aries sa isang malaking kompanya as a secretary.Para sa kanya,mahirap ang kanyang trabaho sapagkat maraming utos ang nakaatang sa kanya.Encode here and there,appointment here and there,at ang mga tambak na papeles na pinapagawa ng boss niyang walang ibang ginawa kundi ang landiin ang mga empleyado niya.Si Stephen Kim.Ang boss niya.Hindi niya alam kung bakit hindi niya magawang umalis sa kompanyang pinagtatrabahuhan niya.Malaki rin naman ang kanyang sweldo ngunit halos siya na ang gumagawa ng mga bagay na dapat si Sir Stephen ang gumagawa.
"This is my job,so,I have to do this" palaging sinasabi ni Aries sa kapatid niyang si Jen.Ang pangalawa sa apat.Tanging si Jen lang ang nakakaintindi sa mga desisyon niya.Kaya kahit na nahihirapan siya sa trabaho niya tinatanggap niya pa rin ito.

BUT

Isang araw,nagising na lamang siya sa tabi ng boss niya.

Hindi niya alam ang nangyari .


Ano kaya ang mga mangyayari pagkatapos ng nangyari sa kanila ng boss niya?Yun ay kung may nangyari nga ba.

title: The Day the World Spun Backwards
description:
"Your outfit is worth more than my whole apartment, or my existence. " Amberleigh retorted sourly, as Gavin troted around the room Touching. Absolutely. Everything.
"Thats the thing about having money," he replied, oblivious to the poison in her voice, " you get to spend it." he touched a picture of her and her sister from a year ago. A very, very, long time ago it seemed.
"Just, sit down. You make me nervous doing that." She itched for him to sit still and shut up for two seconds. He didn't. Gavin decided to make his way to the back of the apartment.
"Gavin! That is off limits, no!" Amberleigh shrieked in fright. Her room was a disaster zone and clothes were everywhere.

title: Frisson (adapter Jortini)
description:
Tini vit dans une petit ville américaine, aux abords d'une forêt. Son enfance a été marquée par l'irruption d'une meute de loups qui l'a attaquée. L'un des animaux l'a sauvée et depuis, un lien étrange s'est établi entre la jeune fille et celoup . Ombre à la fois protectrice et inquiétante, il rôde autour de la maison isolée.

La mort brutale d'un élève du lycée de Tini déclenche une réaction violente: la ville entière crie au loup, et lance des chasseurs à travers la forêt. Tous les animaux ne parviennent pas à échapper aux balles... le loup de Tini est touché.

Quelques heures plus tard, Tini retrouve sur le pas de sa porte un jeune homme, blessé, au regard étrangement familier...

description: I have decided to write a story based upon the ancient magus bride. This manga and the one episode of the anime that has come out so far has very much caught my attention. The apprentices both meet each other and get to know one another, both going through their own hoops of troubles and concerns. I also am gonna include some love fluff between elias and chise as I find them to both be really cute :3 . Bayonetta's apprentice will be named Agnolia. Kinda like the flower, like how in the game, if you die or get hit, Bayonetta and Jeanne have roses spawn. I thought the name would fit perfectly. Furthermore, for Agnolia, her story kinda places her after the events in Bayonetta 2, and how Agnolia saving her life, goes through a portal, making her travel 2000 years into the past.

description:
Faith è una giovane ragazza di 23 anni, derisa spesso per il suo carattere chiuso e differente da molte sue coetanee, fin da bambina.
Una ragazza, chiusa, sulle sue, con uno dei più grandi pesi che oggi giorno si portano addosso, non riuscire ad accettarsi.
Faith non è asociale o senza interessi per le persone, ha semplicemente una grande paura di essere delusa, di nuovo.
Emma è, d'altro canto, una delle ragazze più belle di tutta l'università. Bionda, alta, con uno sguardo azzurro cielo acceso, che incanta molti e soddisfa in pochi.
In tutta la loro diversità, esiste un punto di collisione all'apparenza invisibile che entrambe stanno sfiorando con un dito.
Un punto delineato per dare una svolta definitiva alla loro vita.

title: La Vénus d'Ille de Prosper Mérimée
description: Je sais que cela va vous surprendre que je reprenne une œuvre de Mérimée mais c'est car j'ai eu une bonne note à une rédaction avec ce livre comme thème. Je vous explique: en classe nous avons lu La Vénus d'Ille et notre prof de français nous a demandé de continué l'histoire en imaginant que Mme de Peyrehorade n'avais pas fait fondre la statue en cloche mais l'avais donné au narrateur. Donc vu que j'ai eu une bonne note je me suis <pourquoi ne pas l'écrire sur mon compte wattpad> et c'est se que je fais, je l'écris sur mon compte. Je vais d'abord recopié le livre et après recopier ma suite de l'histoire. Je recopie La Vénus d'Ille pour vous rappeler l'histoire. J'espère que cela vous plaira, merci de partager si l'histoire vous plait et que vous pensez que  vos amis vont aimer. Bisous mes kangourous.

title: PETUALANGANKU DENGAN DIA
description:
Lesa,seorang cewek ceroboh Pendek yang suka bertualang.Sedangkan Veronika dan Leniy tidak.Mereka kerjanya tau apa?Nyari pacar melulu!Leniy bersamaan Simon dan Veronika bersama Leo.Lesa Sebenarnya dah dapat Tapi Ada 2,yaitu Loan dan Eko.Mereka meminta Lesa memilih Salah Satu.
Mereka bersekolah di sekolah methodine Beautiful Campus.Didekat Sana Ada hutan horror yang Sering dibalang orang.Lesa penasaran Akan Hutan Ini.Veronika dan Leniy akhirnya ikut juga dalam petualangan Ini dengan Simon,Leo,Loan dan Eko.

Bagaimana Kisah Selanjutnya?Ikutin teruslah ya!

title: Candidus
description: Ezra in an unusual girl. She has a weird knack for always being right. She gets these weird dreams about people she never met... things that are going to happen, but she never knows when. Many people think that she is a genius but to her its just a gift.... a gift that has more meaning than smarts. She constantly has this dream of this one boy handsome and weirdly quite deadly. When that boy enters her classroom.... all hell breaks loose.

title: One day crush
description:
ONE DAY CRUSH
******************************************
This is a short story of a busy techie over mid twenties who had a crush over a girl of about early twenties passing by him. 

This was happening in a Traffic signal and this was lasted only for a day. 

Everyone has crush on someone.

title: I'm All Yours
description:
Nagmahal.

Naghigante.

Nagmahal ulit.

Pero sa dati parin bang tao na unang nagpatibok sa kanyang puso?

title: story of the misfit bats
description: the story of three teens from my rag tag team ones hot the shadow, batgirl, and jester get their own story of their past present and future read on to find out. don't own anyone else beside a few ocs.
